1) download git
2) download github comfy ui -  внизу будет  direct downlod (portable)
3) устанавливаем python 3.10. 6
4) устанавливаем manager (для плагинов) - comfyUI manager - внизу будет  ссылка bat (для portable) - кидаем в внутрь comfy и запускаем
5) запускам nvidia gpu

6) далее FLUX INSTALL GUIDE
    1) Download t5xxl_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors and clip_l.safetensors from   
        https://huggingface.co/comfyanonymous/flux_text_encoders/tree/main
        Place these files in the ComfyUI/models/clip/ directory.

    If
    you have high vram and ram, you can download the FP16 version 
    (t5xxl_fp16.safetensors) for better results. For lower memory usage, 
    stick with t5xxl_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors.

    2)  Download VAE Model

        Download the VAE model ae.safetensors / ae.sft from https://huggingface.co/black-forest-labs/FLUX.1-schnell/tree/main

        Place the file in the ComfyUI/models/vae/ folder.

    3)  Download UNet Model

        Download flux1-schnell.sft from 
        https://huggingface.co/black-forest-labs/FLUX.1-schnell/tree/main
        

        Place the file in the ComfyUI/models/unet/ folder.

    ---------------------
    если выпадает ошибка: HeaderTooLarge - перекачай файлы
    ---------------------

    ПРОБУЕМ - 01 Flux-Schnell-ComfyUI-Workflow перетянув и настроив по скриншоту